      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience. While it shows some light, expected signs of use, it remains a clean and dependable choice for its next owner. It\u2019s a wonderful opportunity to own a quality car that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
