    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair, functional condition and would make a decent budget-friendly option or a project car for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows noticeable wear including some minor dents and paint fading, while the interior has visible staining and wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, though it may require some upcoming maintenance to address minor fluid leaks and suspension noise. It is a reliable runner for short distances, but a thorough inspection is recommended for long-term peace of mind.",
